   Title="{{R}andomized comparison of {T}-type versus {L}-type calcium-channel blockade on exercise duration in stable angina: results of the {P}osicor {R}eduction of {I}schemia {D}uring {E}xercise ({P}{R}{I}{D}{E}) trial}",
   Journal="Am. Heart J.",
