   Title="{{A}ntihypertensive efficacy of optimally titrated doses of once-daily sustained-release diltiazem: a placebo-controlled trial. {D}{I}{L}{P}{L}{A}{C}{O}{M}{P} {S}tudy {G}roup}",
   Journal="Cardiology",
